---
title: Asian Chicken & Radish Tacos with Creamy Slaw
description: Tacos with inspired by Asian cooking are coming together to make an unbeatable fusion of flavours. We've packed tortillas with oyster sauce-glazed diced chicken and added a colourful slaw with radish for a bit of peppery crunch. It’s the ultimate combination!
